have tried to eliminate

00:15:15.730 --> 00:15:18.580
because flaring of--

00:15:18.580 --> 00:15:22.540
flaring of natural gas
reduces the greenhouse impact

00:15:22.540 --> 00:15:24.815
by about a factor of 20.

00:15:24.815 --> 00:15:26.440
So if you have natural
gas and you just

00:15:26.440 --> 00:15:30.190
