of million dollars, roughly,

00:46:00.880 --> 00:46:05.110
invested in our company was
from fellow Sloan Fellows,

00:46:05.110 --> 00:46:06.658
which was pretty remarkable.

00:46:06.658 --> 00:46:08.200
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
Draper Labs also

00:46:08.200 --> 00:46:09.580
have-- do they have that IP?

00:46:09.580 --> 00:46:09.970
BOB DIMATTEO: Yes.

