Yes.

00:46:10.470 --> 00:46:11.860
Draper Labs involved as well.

00:46:11.860 --> 00:46:13.902
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: And
did they give you the IP

00:46:13.902 --> 00:46:15.490
or do they have the IP?

